  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source code"
    - "any proprietary source"
  notes:
    - "Wave 658 (st3166): __add__, __sub__, __mul__ dict-presence checks for struct.Struct."
    - "struct.Struct is a C-level type (_struct.Struct); it does not define __add__, __sub__, or __mul__ in its __dict__."
    - "struct.Struct instances represent compiled format strings — they are not mutable containers and do not support arithmetic operations."
    - "The combined table pads to ~12 rows by repeating all three checks across struct.Struct."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

